commitResults.messageBody:
Update the Gradle build system to use modern plugins and dependencies.
This includes upgrading the Gradle wrapper to 8.13 and replacing the
deprecated shadow plugin with com.gradleup.shadow:9.0.0-beta9. The
JavaFX plugin has been added with org.openjfx.javafxplugin:0.1.0 to
support modern JavaFX integration, along with a JavaFX runtime upgrade
to 21.0.6. Testing dependencies are also updated with JUnit Jupiter
5.11.4.
